description: Try our easy to follow Blueberry And Banana Muffin recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Blueberry And Banana Muffin Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Divide mixture between pans. Bake for 20-25 minutes or until a skewer inserted into the centre of a muffin comes out clean. Serve spread with cream cheese.
